ThingDef.label: chocolate
ThingDef.description: A delicious preparation of cocoa seeds ground together with sugar and vanilla. It fulfills the need for recreation, but it is not very nutritious.

ThingDef.label: kibble
ThingDef.description: Animal feed made from mixed meat and plant sources. Humans can eat it, but they really, really don't like it.

ThingDef.label: insect jelly
ThingDef.description: Jelly stored and used as food by oversized insects. It is smooth, rich, and fulfills the recreation need of those who consume it. Because of its unique biological properties, it can nourish almost any creature and never rots.
